social_posts.post_text: Wow. In 5.4 million hours you could have watched Terminator 2: Judgement Day 2,131,578 times. thanks for listening to my songs instead

happy 30 to my amazing wife @thekatiestevens. so proud of the person I get to spend my life with. I can’t wait to see you as a mom and everything this next chapter has in store. You were cool in your 20s but I think this next decade is gonna be even better. 😘 love you
we’ll be right here
Merry Quismois from the DiGiovanni’s
Been an epic ride so far with this guy. Can’t wait for the world to hear #bluebirddays all the way through next month
#1 song in the country! Extremely grateful to be a part of another one with @jordandavisofficial. What a song, team, group of musicians, engineers etc. Thanks so much to everyone who listened 🌎

Congrats to my old friend @samhollander for an amazing night in Nashville celebrating the release of #21hitwonder. I’m a lucky guy to be even a small part of your incredible career and certainly wouldn’t be where I am today without ya!
some days can’t be overshadowed by bad weather
One of my favorite lyrics off the new project. Enjoyed every second of producing this one. #moneyisntreal
Bluebird for Bluebird Days. out TOMORROW
poured a lot into this one. proud. #bluebirddays
Out now! Strawberry Wine And A Cheap Six Pack co-written w/ @travisrdenning @thomasarcher01 @jerryflowersmusic co-produced w/ @countryjeremyst

social_posts.post_text: Out today! Wrote “Wish You Would” with @ingridandress and @davebarnesmusic a few years back and the melodies have been popping up in my head ever since. Thanks so much for making it sound amazing Ingrid and @samellismusic
first easter weekend for the little lady

#goceltics

Happy first Mother’s Day to @thekatiestevens! What a year it’s been watching you power through pregnancy and instantly become super mom. Romy is truly the luckiest baby. We will be forever grateful for all your sacrifices, sleepless nights, and seemingly endless days ❤️
congrats to the Dennings!
Thanks so much for choosing to include me in the “Legendary Leominster” display! What a cool moment to spot this photo while driving through the neighborhoods I grew up in.  @deanmazzarella
This year I’m outta town with family, but had to throw it back to my all time favorite #cmafest
mom took us bowling for Father’s day 🎳 #peteweber @thekatiestevens

congrats to @jordandavisofficial on another one! Knew halfway through listening to the demo that this was an incredibly special song. @greylanjames so glad to be a part of your first #1 (of many more to come). @chasemcgillsongwriter and @joshosbornesongwriter you guys are badasses. crazy to think of how many of my favorite moments in town you’ve been involved in. thanks to this incredible band, @jimcooleymix, @randymerrill_sterling, everyone who used their magic to make this song what is
music is too unpredictable. starting her on a more realistic career path 📷:@aishtray

appreciation post. She always gives more than she’s got without hesitation or a single question. I’m so lucky Romy gets to learn it all from this loving soul…

Happy 4 years of marriage to my beautiful wife @thekatiestevens. Whenever I slow down to reflect I can’t believe how fast time is flying by with you. Thank you for being the most amazing human, wife, and now Romy-mom. Swipe right to jump back to wedding, engagement, and first-ish date ❤️
